18:16.562 --> 18:19.224
- One handcuff key coming up.
- Great.

18:19.331 --> 18:22.528
[Belching]

18:22.634 --> 18:24.602
What the hell are you doing?

18:24.703 --> 18:26.933
Swallowed a key just in case
I ended up doing a show.

18:27.039 --> 18:29.769
- <i>[Belching]</i>
- Come on. This is disgusting.

18:29.875 --> 18:32.776
- I'm doing this for you.
