18:32.878 --> 18:34.971
<i>while Michael switched out the coolers.</i>

18:35.080 --> 18:37.446
- Why are you switching out the coolers?
- It buys us time, Dad.

18:37.549 --> 18:39.676
- What? Like a second?
- <i>Don't worry about it, okay?</i>

18:39.785 --> 18:42.618
When I get this evidence out of here,
