18:53.432 --> 18:56.629
Well, that's- that's great.

18:57.669 --> 18:59.227
- <i>[Gags]</i>
- <i>[Clattering]</i>

18:59.338 --> 19:00.965
Now who's a horrible magician?

19:01.073 --> 19:04.975
That is a crown, you horse's ass.

